'''人们会飞'''（有段时间名为'''Epic Games Poland'''），是一家由Adrian Chmielarz成立于2002年2月，总部设在波兰华沙的游戏开发商。该团队目前有20名成员（不包括外部承包商）。

该公司名字是从数张专辑和歌曲标题名称后选择出来的。2007年8月20日，Epic Games收购该公司多数股份。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.joystiq.com/2007/08/20/epic-believes-people-can-fly-acquires-majority-stake/ |title=Epic Games buys People Can Fly studio |access-date=2015-11-16 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/68lOUJsLf?url=http://www.joystiq.com/2007/08/20/epic-believes-people-can-fly-acquires-majority-stake/ |archive-date=2012-06-28 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>在2013年11月1日，公司更名为Epic Games Poland，<Ref>
{{Cite web | url = http://www.polygon.com/2013/11/1/5055008/people-can-fly-now-known-as-epic-games-poland | title = People Can Fly now known as Epic Games Poland | first = Samit | last = Sarkar | date = 2013-11-01 | accessdate = 2013-11-01 | publisher = [[Polygon_(website)|Polygon]] | archive-date = 2013-11-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131102204219/http://www.polygon.com/2013/11/1/5055008/people-can-fly-now-known-as-epic-games-poland | dead-url = no }}
</ref>然而在2015年6月24日，该公司宣布独立并恢复使用旧名称和旧标志。<ref name="gamespot2">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/people-can-fly-turns-independent-buys-bulletstorm-/1100-6428420/|title=People Can Fly Turns Independent, Buys Bulletstorm IP|first=Tamoor|last=Hussain|work=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|date=June 24, 2015|accessdate=June 24, 2015|archive-date=2015-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150627044206/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/people-can-fly-turns-independent-buys-bulletstorm-/1100-6428420/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

